{"tid":1440053,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【討論】關於手足舉英、美、國旗問題","createTime":"2019-08-10T10:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:46:18.000Z","uid":260300,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"05652c4242df28a17fa4c34e0b13e0b450c240a5","tid":1440053,"uid":260300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"在修例風波兩個月之後，港共政府無能，眼看無法控制局面。<br />\n<br />\n港共政府，大陸、香港紅媚製造<span style=\"color: red;\">輿論</span>慾將我們批鬥為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港獨分子</span></span>，外國勢力控制學生等等，而我們手足舉英、美國旗時，反而正中紅媒下懷。<br />\n<br />\n大陸、香港紅媒大肆宣傳我們手足手舉外國旗幟圖像，無腦藍絲即刻腦充血認為我們乜咩乜分裂國家，做外國走狗。大陸玻璃心更不用講，玻璃心碎裂到滿地，全身滲血。<br />\n<br />\n其實我們大家都很了解自己的訴求，就是<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span>，<br />\n<br />\n那這樣是不是就不要舉外國旗?錯！更加要舉！<br />\n我們可以舉<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全球各個民主國家</span></span>的旗幟！！！<br />\n<br />\n其中主要可以舉<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聯合國旗幟</span></span>。<br />\n我們要表達是香港在共產黨的壓迫下，香港人民追求民主，自由的希望。香港人民希望引起<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">全球各個民主國家</span></span>的關注<br />\n希望各個國家可以在聯合國上提及香港問題。<br />\n這不是中國內政，這是<span style=\"color: red;\">人權</span>問題！<span style=\"color: red;\">每一個聯合國會員國</span>都有權提起。<br />\n<br />\n所以我們要高舉<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聯合國</span></span>旗幟，讓每個聯合國會員國關注<br />\n<br />\n這樣也不會一味被紅媒批鬥為<span style=\"color: red;\">港獨</span><br />\n<br />\n這也只是我一個小市民愚見，有任何問題請大家多多指教<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得無用  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804215ad356e97c56acd1580c7537c901f95ca15","tid":1440053,"uid":260300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:21:47.000Z","msg":"很少發帖，自推五次，無人關注由佢沉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52926aa2a28a0a222b86e1fdabf092804252e145","tid":1440053,"uid":260300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15283140b3a796bf0c10810907de2714f9ccbc9","tid":1440053,"uid":127328,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:24:04.000Z","msg":"我全力支持舉支拿 外所有旗<br />\n旗唔係比中共睇<br />\n係比全球睇，令香港得到佢地支援<br />\n所以切勿被<span style=\"color: red;\">中國分化</span><br />\n全部都係同路人！"},{"pid":"63bab3b687e107f5001d7b24774fe92c143a3d33","tid":1440053,"uid":260300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19cc388d4f8937ffe14f40d7101fd20082b26b7d","tid":1440053,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:26:17.000Z","msg":"唔同意前半<br />\n不過覺得可以舉下"},{"pid":"61986cf34ae9a43527d4ef400ddaccc2114d592f","tid":1440053,"uid":260300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:26:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"396c201a63bfe17b7f58c232ef753ab571e6d596","tid":1440053,"uid":204929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:26:41.000Z","msg":"如果淨係舉一個國家嘅旗, 咁樣似暗示緊<br />\n香港人想香港主權係屬於邊個!"},{"pid":"640d251ab486ffe9988d7c0ae499fad4163f5036","tid":1440053,"uid":260300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:27:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e50784fd355e819dc8ea548fef320cddb4a084c2","tid":1440053,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:28:03.000Z","msg":"同埋聯合國中国都係聯合國會員， 唔係好建議"},{"pid":"ad5336885590e93a7bdb1db8c6fd2ca838b4a005","tid":1440053,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"要舉就自己出去舉"},{"pid":"2cc456848ac81f1a6b32bd1df9a7bd1da28616be","tid":1440053,"uid":260300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:29:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f61afbaf673472d77d296dec18426db5f76cea7","tid":1440053,"uid":260300,